  "title": "Sales & Marketing Trainee (Entry Level – Fast Track Growth)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Sales & Marketing Executive (ENTRY LEVEL  – Performance-Based Growth)</strong></em><br /><br />Ready to build a results-driven career in sales and marketing where advancement is earned through performance, not tenure? Ascend Marketing Solutions is seeking driven individuals to represent leading brands and deliver high-impact, face-to-face marketing campaigns across Singapore.<br /><br />This role is designed for candidates who value professional development, measurable results, and accelerated career progression within a competitive environment.</p><p><u>Your Role</u><br />- Execute strategic sales and marketing campaigns with a strong focus on customer engagement<br />- Represent premium brands while building lasting client relationships<br />- Identify market opportunities to drive brand growth and visibility<br />- Collaborate with a high-performing team to consistently exceed targets</p><p><u>Why Ascend Marketing Solutions</u><br />- Clearly defined, performance-based career progression<br />- Competitive, uncapped earning structure<br />- Regional exposure and leadership development opportunities<br />- Structured coaching, mentorship, and professional training<br />- Performance-focused, supportive, and growth-oriented culture</p><p><u>Who We’re Looking For</u><br />- Strong communication and interpersonal skills<br />- Background in sales, marketing, or customer-facing roles is an advantage<br />- Highly motivated, coachable, and results-oriented individuals</p><p><em><strong>Apply now to accelerate your career with Ascend Marketing Solutions.</strong></em></p>",
